Usage

advs

A data frame with 40702 rows and 78 variables:

Sequence Number

Vital Signs Test Name

Original Units

VSSTRESU

Standard Units

VSSTAT

Completion Status

VSLOC

Location of Vital Signs Measurement

VSBLFL

Baseline Flag

VISITNUM

Visit Number

VISIT

Visit Name

VISITDY

Planned Study Day of Visit

VSDTC

Date/Time of Measurements

VSDY

Study Day of Vital Signs

VSTPT

VSTPTNUM

Planned Time Point Number

VSELTM

Planned Elapsed Time from Time Point Ref

VSTPTREF

Time Point Reference

ADT

Analysis Date

ADY

PARAMCD

Parameter Code

Analysis Value

ATPTN

Analysis Reference Range Indicator
